<Layout title="App FAQ - RoyalPrompts" description="Frequently asked questions about RoyalPrompts mobile app - Privacy, usage, and safety information.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">RoyalPrompts App FAQ</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Common questions about RoyalPrompts mobile app. If you don't find your answer here, contact us at support@royalprompts.online
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üîí Is RoyalPrompts safe to use?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes! RoyalPrompts is completely safe. We use anonymous login, don't collect personal information, and follow strict privacy practices. The app is safe for all ages.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üì± Do I need to create an account?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            No account needed! RoyalPrompts uses anonymous login. Just download the app and start using it immediately. No email, password, or personal information required.
