            <li>‚Ä¢ Anonymous device ID (no personal info)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ App version and device type</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Basic usage statistics</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Crash reports (to fix bugs)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
            We DON'T collect names, emails, location, photos, or any personal information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üë∂ Is RoyalPrompts safe for children?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes! RoyalPrompts is safe for all ages. We don't collect personal information from anyone, including children under 13. Children can use the app with parental supervision.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üÜì Is RoyalPrompts really free?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, RoyalPrompts is completely free to download and use. No hidden fees, no subscriptions, no in-app purchases. All features are available at no cost.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üóëÔ∏è How do I delete my data?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Deleting your data is easy:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Uninstall the app (removes all local data)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Clear app data in your device settings</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Email us at privacy@royalprompts.online to delete server data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üåê Does RoyalPrompts need internet?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            RoyalPrompts works offline for saved prompts and favorites. Internet is needed to:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Download new prompts</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Sync data across devices</li>
