          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üì± Can I use RoyalPrompts on multiple devices?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes! You can use RoyalPrompts on multiple devices. Your favorites and created prompts will sync across devices using your anonymous device ID.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
