          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Email: support@royalprompts.online</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Privacy questions: privacy@royalprompts.online</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Response time: Within 48 hours</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üîÑ How often is the app updated?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We regularly update RoyalPrompts to add new features, fix bugs, and improve performance. Updates are automatic through the app store.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">üéØ What can I use RoyalPrompts for?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            RoyalPrompts is perfect for:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Creative writing projects</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Blog posts and articles</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Social media content</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Business communications</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Academic writing</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Personal journaling</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Any writing that needs inspiration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">‚öñÔ∏è Can I use prompts commercially?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes! You can use RoyalPrompts prompts for personal and commercial projects. The prompts are provided for your use, and any content you create belongs to you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mt-12">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
