            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
              <strong>Still have questions?</strong> Don't hesitate to contact us at support@royalprompts.online. We're here to help and respond within 48 hours.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
